Hello, I’m Alexander from HostUS. HostUS is owned and operated by HostUS Solutions LLC, and we are a registered LLC in Delaware, USA. We are long established, having provided hosting services since 2012.&lt;br&gt;


Thanks to everyone that voted for us in the most recent LowEndTalk provider poll! Coming in 9th meant a lot to me, and to the team at HostUS. It's with that showing and the good reception of our Hong Kong product launch earlier this year that I am happy to announce....&lt;br&gt;

&lt;b style="margin:auto"&gt;&lt;u&gt;London as our 5th location&lt;/u&gt;, which is also our first step in expanding across Europe&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;

But... it does not stop there!&lt;br&gt;

&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;London we've turbo-charged for the speed freaks. We are providing a &lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;shared 10Gbps connection&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt; to every VPS in London. Yes, up to TEN gigabits per second in every VPS container (fair use of course).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;To further sweeten the deal, all London VPS include &lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;FREE Basic DDoS Protection&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt;. This location is &lt;b&gt;&lt;u&gt;protected from DDoS attacks up to 20Gbps&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/b&gt; with on-network protection provided by Arbor TMS hardware.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We've put some big iron behind the new UK launch. London is running on Dual Xeon E5 v3 CPUs. These big CPUs are bundled with plenty of DDR4 RAM, hardware RAID 10, and SSD caching.
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

